summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Block 15, West Side heights; Section 1, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Lots 1 and 2, Block 5, Linsley's Mineral Springs Plat; Vacated Alley in block 5, A.A.
